Crystal Asige is set to make her debut single after she left Sauti Sol's record label Sol Generation. Asige wowed fans with her melodious voice in the hit song, ‘Extravaganza’. She is set to host a pre-release event live ahead of the full music video release on Saturday. Speaking to Word Is early this year, Bien said Asige left the label amicably. "We are not working with Crystal anymore and this came with a lot of complications. It was an amicable break and we are glad we gave her a platform," he said. Asige is also a songwriter, producer, YouTuber and VIP ambassador.